{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "13-late-codes-quizlock-frontend-integration",
    "name": "QuizLock API — 13. Late Codes",
    "description": "Module 13 — Late Codes (Codes de retard)\n\nPermet de générer des codes de bypass pour qu'un élève puisse passer un examen une fois la deadline dépassée.\n\n1. Teacher : Générer\n2. Student : Valider\n\n**Auth** : Cookie next-auth.session-token\n**Base URL** : {{baseUrl}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "examId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "studentId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "lateCode",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Générer code retard (Teacher)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    var res = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (res.lateCode && res.lateCode.code) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('lateCode', res.lateCode.code);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/late-codes/generate",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "late-codes", "generate"]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"examId\": \"{{examId}}\",\n  \"usagesRemaining\": 1,\n  \"assignedUserId\": \"{{studentId}}\",\n  \"reason\": \"Orage / coupure d'électricité\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "POST /api/late-codes/generate\n\nCrée ce code unique de 8 caractères."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Valider code retard (Student)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/late-codes/validate",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "late-codes", "validate"]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"examId\": \"{{examId}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{lateCode}}\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "POST /api/late-codes/validate\n\nÀ appeler par l'étudiant dans le lobby d'un examen expiré afin de le débloquer."
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ]
}
